ource/Meta_Platforms\"}, {\"begin\": 2219, \"end\": 2225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1717791711950659e-39, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics coverage will include more elements like behind-the-scenes footage and pop culture discussion to encompass the most popular genres across television, NBCUniversal executives said.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2410, \"end\": 2422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999116718648748, \"rank\": 8.833593673691103e-05, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One highlight reel featured rapper Cardi B meeting with American track and field sprinter Sha'Carri Richardson.\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2497, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.111682961494545e-11, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2531, \"end\": 2551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will have the best drama, the best reality and the best comedy show all rolled into one,\\\" said Rick Cordella, president of NBC Sp